{"tid":2186191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係好驚尷尬架？","createTime":"2020-09-02T18:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:44:53.000Z","uid":282619,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9b589d894e107bdcf196ab679c9be1cf9cdb36","tid":2186191,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:28:00.000Z","msg":"係驚到一個點，例如會因為驚尷尬都唔去示愛<br />\n同佢講完我愛你，可唔可以做我女朋友呢啲我係永遠唔會講既，因為講完好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會覺得，講完，咁點，人哋話好，咁你點應，直接拖手？又好似好小朋友。鍚落去？又好似太快。呢個我覺得係一個好尷尬既位，表白完我覺唔會有一大段時間會處於尷尬，無論佢答應與否都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連如果我覺得我覆得好尷尬既信息，我會del對話掩耳盜鈴咁當無send過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人同我一樣，係驚尷尬驚到直頭要逃避尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e84d594bc356de7b052c82b4c57aab6e59b706","tid":2186191,"uid":254967,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:30:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89f8377ac0fadb621ab24e9301bdc0fc132ca789","tid":2186191,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"646b3b85444a92b53f4e1ce8a3b64f586e88458d","tid":2186191,"uid":282619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89f8377ac0fadb621ab24e9301bdc0fc132ca789","tid":2186191,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:31:09.000Z","msg":"小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18:40:58.000Z","msg":"又係你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca2ea9d7a40a6bb7ae5a1ebf02d15aac34245af","tid":2186191,"uid":282619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89f8377ac0fadb621ab24e9301bdc0fc132ca789","tid":2186191,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T18